    <has_dmc>Yes</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Polycystic ovary syndrome (PCOS) is associated with an increased cardiovascular risk. The aim
      of the study was to evaluate long-term effects of inositol on some cardiovascular risk
      factors in PCOS patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
