  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Polycystic Ovary Syndrome

          -  Age &gt;18 and &lt;35

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Chronic or acute inflammatory disease, cancer, autoimmune disease, treatment during
             the last 6 months prior to our evaluation, DM2, hypertension, major surgery in the
             last 3 months or other hormonal dysfunctions (hypothalamic, pituitary, thyroidal, or
             adrenal causes).
      </textblock>
